<br>
Bertoxxulous (black sapphire): AC 4, WIS 5, INT 5, mana 40, sv disease 9, trivial &gt;250 <br>
<br>
Note that 2 or 3 tries may be needed for a GM potter and as it requires black saphires (imbued by a bertox cleric) this will likely be more expensive than the standard price of 1500 pp for  a golden idol. Further, there is continuing debate as to the exsistance of a 29 plus bertox cleric on FV.<br>
<br>
I am a GM potter.  If you supply the imbued stones I would charge you 1500 to make one.<br>
<br>
